results.name: Decimal expansion of sqrt(16394397).
comment: Continued fraction expansion of sqrt(16394397) is 4048 followed by (repeat 1, 2023, 2, 2023, 1, 8096).
xref: Cf. A002194 (decimal expansion of sqrt(3)), A010475 (decimal expansion of sqrt(19)), A010523 (decimal expansion of sqrt(71)), A176715 (decimal expansion of sqrt(4051)), A176713 (decimal expansion of (4047+sqrt(16394397))/142).
